    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "この喫茶店、いつも通るのに初めて入りました\n東京に行く時はいつもバタバタしてるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I entered this cafe for the first time‚ even though I always pass by it.\nI'm always in a rush when I go to Tokyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "この距離を毎回往復してる奥山さんは凄いな……\nそうだ、先方との打ち合わせの感触はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's amazing that you travel this distance back and forth every time‚ Okuyama-san.\nBy the way‚ how was the meeting with the association?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "とっっっても楽しかったです！　リハをした撮影現場が\n子役の時と同じ場所で本当に懐かしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so much fun! The rehearsal and filming took place\nin the same location as when I was a child actor‚ and it felt nostalgic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "何よりみなさん、とっても温かくもてなしてくれて\nびっくりしちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Above all‚ everyone was very warm and welcoming‚\nand I was surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、バンプロにいた頃からオファーをかけていて\n何度も断られてた……っていう話は驚いたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they had been offering you the job since your time at Van Production‚\nand you had rejected it multiple times… that was surprising.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうどトリエルの活動が本格化した時期で\nスケジュールが合わなかったらしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was around the time TRINITYAiLE's activities were intensifying‚\nand it seems the schedules didn't align.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、私達に知らされていなかったとはいえ\n申し訳ないことをしちゃいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's true. Although we weren't informed‚\nI feel sorry about that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、奥山さんが組合の方の\n顔と名前をみんな覚えてて驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I was amazed that Okuyama-san remembered the faces and names\nof the association members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとした特技なんです、えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a little skill of mine‚ hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "「アイドルになった今も、テレビで欠かさず観てます」\nって言ってもらえて嬉しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was happy to hear them say‚\n\"Even now as an idol‚ we watch you on TV all the time.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんは組合の方に愛されてるなって思ったよ\nみんな娘や孫を見るみたいな優しい目をしてた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought Okuyama-san is loved by the association members‚\nthey had kind eyes‚ as if they were looking at their own daughter or grandchild.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそんな感じでしたね。握手しながら\n「ぜひうちの孫の嫁に」って何度か言われましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ it felt that way. While shaking hands‚\nthey said‚ \"Please be my grandchild's wife\" a few times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "事務所にトリエルのポスターも沢山貼ってあったし\n奥山さんは山形のスターなんだなって改めて感じたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were many TRINITYAiLE posters in the office too‚\nI felt once again that Okuyama-san is a star in Yamagata.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう、あんまり褒めないで下さいよー！\n顏が熱くなってきちゃいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-Please don't praise me too much!\nMy face is getting hot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん。ところで、CMの内容はどう思った？\n正直な意見を聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. By the way‚ what did you think of the commercial content?\nGive me your honest opinion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "凄くいいと思いました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was really great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "山形名産のさくらんぼを使ったスイーツを食レポしつつ\n私のナレーションを重ねる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did a taste review of sweets made with Yamagata's famous cherries‚\noverlaying it with my narration…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "どちらも私の声で、演じ分けるっていうのが\n凄く面白いなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of them using my voice and portraying different characters‚\nI found it very interesting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "セリフのパターンが用意されていて\nどれを選んでもいいと言われましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were prepared patterns for the lines‚\nand they said I could choose any of them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "可愛さ重視のものもあればコミカルなものもあって\n真面目なパターンも……うーん、迷っちゃいますねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Some were focused on cuteness‚ some were comical‚\nand there were serious patterns too… hmm‚ it's a dilemma.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい悩みだな\nお、そろそろ新幹線の時間だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a delightful dilemma.\nOh‚ it's about time for the Shinkansen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、新幹線の中でじっくり考えてみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ I'll think about it carefully on the Shinkansen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 158.8666666667
    },
    {
